Where is there such a description? Is there a wiki page that can be pointed to in the JIRA tickets? Or some other review? There's an mp4 file pointed at in the comments of DCAEGEN2-2819, but it is inaccessible.

How can I tell whether the proper stuff is being implemented without this information?
